Kate Bosworth looked every inch the elegant bride in an ivory satin strapless gown when she tied the knot with Michael Polish in Philipsburg, Montana on Saturday.

Now,
in newly-released Vogue  footage from fittings with her wedding dress 
designer Oscar de la Renta, we see the 30-year-old's emotional reaction the first time she saw herself in her gown.

'Seeing the dress I was totally shocked at my complete lack of control over my emotions in that moment,' she said. 

