In turn, Mr de la Renta says he is delighted to have been tasked with the job.

'I am extremely honored that you chose me,' he says. 'It's probably the most special day in any woman's life, so I'm very excited to be involved in this.'

Like any other bride-to-be, the actress seemed as though she couldn't wait to open up about her wedding plans.

'Michael
and I talk about this a lot - I think there's two ways that we'll both 
go it'll either be very emotional or we'll just kinda start laughing. . . ' 
she said.

